org.apromore.canoniser

Class DefaultAbstractCanoniser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apromore.plugin.impl.DefaultPlugin
      • org.apromore.plugin.impl.DefaultPropertyAwarePlugin
        • org.apromore.canoniser.DefaultAbstractCanoniser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Canoniser, Plugin, PropertyAwarePlugin

    public abstract class DefaultAbstractCanoniser
extends DefaultPropertyAwarePlugin
implements Canoniser
    Implements common functionality shared by all Canonisers and reads the supported native type from the Canonisers 'plugin.config' file. The key used is: 'canoniser.nativeType'.
    Author:
    Felix Mannhardt (Bonn-Rhein-Sieg University oAS)
